183
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,039
My lord,

184
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,879
since the Night Deity died,

185
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,679
the world enjoys peace

186
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:26,240
and people live prosperously.

187
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:28,879
What a joy!

188
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,600
What about today's offerings?

189
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,039
Have they increased?

190
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:34,200
Offerings remain sufficient,

191
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,360
but are decreasing day by day.

192
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,279
The Night Deity died,

193
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:42,399
and people live securely,

194
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,879
so they needn't make daily offerings.

195
00:11:45,139 --> 00:11:46,700
This is their blessing

196
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,240
and immortal sect's fortune.

197
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,639
I understand.

198
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:51,759
You may leave.

199
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,519
Yes.

200
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,980
Luckily, I have a backup plan.

201
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:32,080
Keeping you alive is really useful.

202
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,000
(Bai Xiaoying.)

203
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,200
(Bai Xiaoying.)

204
00:12:45,059 --> 00:12:46,840
(Bai Xiaoying.)

205
00:12:47,299 --> 00:12:48,980
(Bai Xiaoying.)

206
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,500
(Bai Xiaoying.)

207
00:12:59,279 --> 00:13:01,000
Why do I still dream of the Night Deity?

208
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:08,480
My lord,

209
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,080
do you need my help?

210
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:14,080
Yes.

211
00:13:15,139 --> 00:13:16,580
It's a cushy job

212
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:20,840
that will make your name.

213
00:13:21,639 --> 00:13:22,519
Thank you.

214
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:56,580
Seems I need more.

215
00:13:57,899 --> 00:13:59,620
But before that,

216
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:03,740
I must make more preparations.

217
00:14:04,899 --> 00:14:05,659
Go ahead!

218
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:08,899
Xiaoying.

219
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,179
Try this. It's sweet.

220
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:18,899
True.

221
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:31,720
Look!

222
00:14:31,879 --> 00:14:34,620
Aren't those War God Bai Xiaoying
and Night Deity Ye Chenyuan?

223
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:37,139
Why are they so intimate?

224
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,600
How could the War God
and Night Deity be lovers?

225
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:40,919
Impossible!

226
00:14:41,019 --> 00:14:44,159
The War God can't be a lover
to that ancient evil.

227
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:46,159
The Night Deity was evil!

228
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:48,460
Look over there!

229
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,100
It's really her.

230
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,679
They were lovers.

231
00:14:57,059 --> 00:14:57,940
Who did it?

232
00:14:58,139 --> 00:14:59,940
It's obvious

233
00:15:00,179 --> 00:15:02,779
that the War God and Night Deity
were lovers.

234
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:04,460
Unbelievable!

235
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:05,740
Who could have imagined

236
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:08,050
the War God who should
protect the Three Realms

237
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:10,340
would collude with the Night Deity.

238
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:12,080
Disgusting!

239
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:13,740
You!

240
00:15:17,779 --> 00:15:18,539
War God.

241
00:15:19,279 --> 00:15:20,840
Are you feeling guilty?

242
00:15:21,299 --> 00:15:22,419
If this weren't true,

243
00:15:22,779 --> 00:15:24,580
why did you shatter
the evidence quickly?

244
00:15:25,019 --> 00:15:26,779
- Exactly!
- Absolutely!

245
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:27,700
Guilty, right?

246
00:15:28,259 --> 00:15:29,820
So it's all true.

247
00:15:30,139 --> 00:15:31,940
I wondered how a young girl

248
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,019
became the War God.

249
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,940
So there's a huge secret!

250
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,139
Exactly.

251
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,179
Silence, all of you!

252
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:39,240
Xiaoying.

253
00:15:39,559 --> 00:15:40,159
Don't mind it.

254
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:41,059
Let's go.

255
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,000
She's definitely guilty.

256
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,600
Next,

257
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:02,399
the Night Clan.

258
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,879
(Bai Xiaoying.)

259
00:16:12,559 --> 00:16:13,399
(Bai Xiaoying.)

260
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:20,120
(I'm right here.)

261
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,480
Night Deity?

262
00:16:26,919 --> 00:16:28,000
Why are you here?

263
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:33,539
You summoned me here.

264
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:35,240
Bai Xiaoying.

265
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:37,639
You must feel indignant.

266
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:39,799
I don't understand.

267
00:16:40,299 --> 00:16:42,360
You must be agonizing.

268
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,919
You simply loved Ye Chenyuan.

269
00:16:46,519 --> 00:16:48,480
Why would others hinder you?

270
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:52,019
Have those foolish humans disliked you?

271
00:16:52,179 --> 00:16:52,980
It's their problem,

272
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:54,799
not mine.

273
00:16:55,139 --> 00:16:56,960
Do you really think that way?

274
00:16:59,799 --> 00:17:02,480
Don't you care
even if the Snowfall Valley

275
00:17:02,659 --> 00:17:03,899
perishes?

276
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:05,279
Shut up!

277
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:16,839
(Why do I keep dreaming
of the Night Deity?)

278
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,920
(There must be a reason.)

279
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,559
(I think the Night Deity died.)

280
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,039
(Is Ye Chenyuan)

281
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,880
(still alive?)

282
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:28,640
(But if he is,)

283
00:17:28,799 --> 00:17:30,000
(why doesn't he come find me?)

284
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,160
(Perhaps,)

285
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,440
(the Night Clan knows something.)

